Features.Title: HEPA Filter
Features.Description: Standing for high-efficiency particulate air, the HEPA filter can efficiently remove allergens, including dust, pollen, and pet dander, from your home. These allergens are collected, filtered, and removed from the air, helping you breathe a lot easier.

Features.Title: Cleaner air as you sleep
Features.Description: Thanks to the built-in night mode, the air purifier rapidly prepares your bedroom air for sleep and constantly monitors your bedroom air quality, delivering clean air while you sleep. The dimmed and/or switched off lights and the low sound help you and your family sleep better.

Features.Title: Change filter indicator
Features.Description: To ensure that your unit continues to function at optimal levels over time, replacing the filter is a must. Thanks to the ‘Filter change indicator’ built into the unit, all you need to do is wait for the indicator to light up and replace accordingly, removing any worry of accidentally forgetting.

Features.Title: 2 Year Manufacturer's Warranty
Features.Description: A 24-month parts and labour Manufacturer's warranty is included, giving you that extra peace of mind with this everyday appliance.

FeatureTabData.ProductDescription:
From the home to the office, the Winix Zero+ Pro 5-Stage Air Purifier offers powerful filtering so you can breathe easy.

The comprehensive 5-stage filtration effectively purifies air, removing common pollutants and allergens such as dust, pollen, dande, smoke, odours, and more. Equipped with an Australian hospital-grade true HEPA filter, this can capture pollutants as small as 0.3 microns. The PlasmaWave technology neutralises bacteria, viruses, and harmful gases to give you peace of mind. Plus, this unit keeps offensive odours at bay thanks to the Deodorisation Activated Carbon Corrugated Filter.

Easy to use, you can adjust between four fan speeds or activate the set and forget auto mode. You can also rely on the Triple Smart Sensor to monitor and adjust to changing needs. If you’re using this purifier in the bedroom, the Sleep Mode dims the lights and is designed to operate quietly so you can rest and recharge peacefully.

So whether you or other household members are asthma and hay fever sufferers, or you’re a pet owner, this air purifier can help you sleep better, feel better, and live better.
